[PD PPS Compatible] This USB-C charger uses PPS in addition to Power Delivery. PPS is what Samsung uses for the faster charging speeds, so you will for sure get the full 25W charging to charger your Samsung.

[6Ft C Charger Cable Fast Charging]The attached USB-C to USB-C cables are 6-foot long, which is long enough to stretch from a wall socket to the sofa or from your in-car charger to the kids’ tablet in the back seat. Also, them come with 480Mbps data transfer speeds to ensure a fast and smooth transmission of power and data.

[Universal Compatibility] This type c charger fast charging is designed for Samsung devices, delivering your desired charging speed to Galaxy S23 Ultra / S23+ / S23 / S22 Ultra / S22+ / S22 / S21/ S21+ / S21 Ultra / Z Flip / S10 series/ S9 series/ S8 series / Note 20 series / 10 series / 9 / Samsung Galaxy Tab S7 / S7+ / Tab A series / Samsung Galaxy Buds / Galaxy Watch and more.

[Superior Safety] Conforms to the ETL safety standard, this fast charger type c features a total of 10 safety features including short-circuit protection, high-voltage protection, and temperature control so that you can rest easy while charging your devices.
[What You Get] 2 Pack of 25W USB C Fast Charger with 6ft USB-C to USB-C Cable, our worry-free 24-month warranty, and friendly customer service.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Why Choose this Charger? Fast Charging: This is a USB-C PD charger that can charge up to 25W and it can fully charge a Galaxy S22 in under 1.5 hours.PD PPS Compatible: This Type C charger features Programmable Power Supply (PPS), an extra protocol within Power Delivery (PD) used by Samsung. Super Fast Android Charger This solid and safe USB C charger block can charge up to 25W, which can fully charge a Galaxy S22 in under 1.5 hours. Long Type C Charger Cord The 6-foot cable gives all your outlets easy accessibility so that you can reach from the floor socket to the sofa without you having to sit in an awkward position. Durable C Charger Cable The attached USB-C to USB-C charger is lab-tested to withstand 10,000 bends, lasting ten times longer than lesser cables.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 6, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great charger for the price!
reviews.reviewText: I've purchased multiple chargers over the years. Cheap ones and expensive ones but this charger has surpassed them all. The price is awesome for 2 chargers and it chargers my phone fast and the phone actually holds the charge now. For months my phone was going from 100% to 50% within 30 mins after charging. Then it would slowly go down from there but after charging my phone once with this charger it went down at a normal rate. I'm so glad I purchased this! I do recommend it! I just got it today but I'm hopeful it continues to work for a while...
